<t24help>
<header>
<product>AM</product>
<table>AM.RECOMMENDATION</table>
</header>
<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p />
            <p>Assign a rating to a security.</p>
            <p>Recommendation can be global or specified by an investment objective or a size.</p>
            <p>  example: </p>
            <p />
            <p>0000107-000.ALL.ALL    BUY    / recommend buy</p>
            <p />
            <p>0000086-000.BALANCED.ALL    SBUY    / recommend strong buy for BALANCED investment objective</p>
            <p />
            <p>0000086-000.ALL.SMALL    BUY    / recommend buy for SMALL sizing</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
        </ovdesc>
<ovimage></ovimage>
</overview>
<menu>
<t>
<field>SIZING</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Sizing code extracted automatically from the ID ( field 0).</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>0        12 Alphanumeric characters (No input field)</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>SECURITY</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Security number extracted automatically from the ID (field 0).</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>0        12 Alphanumeric characters (No input field)</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>TARGET.WEIGHT</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Specifies the target percentage for a selected security.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>0        10 numeric characters (Optional input)</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>SECURITY.CURRENCY</field>
<desc>
            <p>Help Text for this field is unavailable.  Please refer to the T24 User Guides for further information.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>RATING</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Defines the rate to assign to a recommended security.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>Mandatory       input. </p>
            <p>Must       exist as a rating code record</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>2        10 Alphanumeric characters</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>INV.OBJECTIVE</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Investment objective extracted automatically from the ID (field 0).</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>0        12 Alphanumeric characters (No input field)</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>TO.DATE</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>The date Recommendation security ended.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>Standard       date format (Optional input)</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>Must       be greater than the date input in the FROM.DATE field</p>
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>RECOMMENDATION.NO</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Unique code which identifies the RECOMMENDATION record. It is keyed on three elements :</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>-</p>
            <p />
            <p>the SECURITY NUMBER</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>-</p>
            <p />
            <p>the INVESTMENT OBJECTIVE or ALL</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>-</p>
            <p />
            <p>and the SIZING or ALL.</p>
            <p />
            <p>Example : 000003-000.GROWTH.SMALL-US</p>
            <p />
            <p>Note</p>
            <p> : only the SECURITY NUMBER input is mandatory. INVESTMENT OBJECTIVE and SIZING are defaulted to ALL if no input.</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>1  45       alphanumeric characters</p>
            <p />
            <p>Mandatory       input. Must be unique as a RECOMMENDATION record</p>
            <p />
            <p />
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>NARRATIVE</field>
<desc>
            <p />
            <p>Contains details of the RECOMMENDATION security.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>35       alphanumeric characters long free format</p>
            <p />
            <p />
            <p>Optional       input</p>
        </desc>
</t>
